      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好问题。SignalMessage是用于视图层TabOverview的，不是由Model直接emit的。TabOverview需要connect到所有四种信号类：SignalMessage、SignalControl、SignalStatus和SignalClosedLoopControlMode，用于接收和显示信号数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabOverview",
        "SignalMessage",
